metadata.description:
Flying cars and skyscrapers with outdoor walkways, My view of Dubai in 2075.
Published in July 29th 2021 on my Behance Portfolio: https://www.behance.net/gallery/124356837/DXB-2075 The image was shared in many pages and Featured on Arabic CNN: https://arabic.cnn.com/style/article/2021/09/26/dubai-future-2075
